com.verygoodsecurity.vgscollect.view.card

Enum FieldType


  • public enum FieldType

    The enum class represents all available type of VGS input fields.

    • Enum Constant Detail

      • CARD_NUMBER

        public static FieldType CARD_NUMBER

        Represents field with card number input in '0000 0000 0000 0000' format. The field supports smart detection of different card brands. Some available brands support Luhn algorithm during validation.

        See Also:
        enum CardType

      • CVC

        public static FieldType CVC

        Represents field with CVC number. CVC input field depends on CARD_NUMBER field. CVC input field applies limitations defined in the CardType class.

        See Also:
        enum CardType

      • CARD_EXPIRATION_DATE

        public static FieldType CARD_EXPIRATION_DATE

        The input field provides date limitations with format MM/yy .

      • CARD_HOLDER_NAME

        public static FieldType CARD_HOLDER_NAME

        The input field applies any characters, digits, and space.

      • INFO

        public static FieldType INFO

        The input field has no limitations.
